        <ul>
                        <li>April 28, <strong style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 16px;"><a href="http://www.cgv.com/dyn/music">Music at the Vineyards</a>, Sunday, 1:00 - 4:00 p.m.</strong><strong style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;- Johnny Neri Duo - </strong><strong style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 16px;">Classic and Contemporary Rock</strong>
